The paper deals with medical imaging observations and uses deep learning techniques to predict tumor growth. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of Convolutional LSTMs, which are a type of recurrent neural network, indicating that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Lastly, the paper deals with medical imaging data, which falls under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
